{"description":"Classes annotated with lombok\u0027s annotation {{@lombok.EqualsAndHashCode}}, {{@lombok.Data}} or {{@lombok.Value}} should be ignored, as the {{equals}} and {{hashCode}} methods will be generated.\r\n\r\n{code}\r\nimport lombok.EqualsAndHashCode;\r\n\r\n@EqualsAndHashCode(callSuper\u003dtrue)\r\nclass Child extends Parent { // Should be compliant\r\n  int foo;\r\n  // ...\r\n}\r\n\r\n@EqualsAndHashCode\r\nclass GrandChild extends Child { // Should be compliant\r\n  int bar;\r\n  // ...\r\n}\r\n{code}","component":"SonarJava","component_version":"3.12"}